00:32:02.199 --> 00:32:09.000
end, we have found that the health authorities are open for our submissions and would like to know

00:32:09.400 --> 00:32:16.280
that the package has been validated. To facilitate a smooth review process,

00:32:16.280 --> 00:32:22.199
it is critical to secure agreement through the prior communication with the health authorities.

00:32:23.640 --> 00:32:29.719
And then based on our case, we can see that the path for the end to end R submission has

00:32:29.719 --> 00:32:37.079
been established, and it takes limited actual efforts for the applicants to implement the

00:32:37.079 --> 00:32:44.839
practice using R with the open source and appropriately disclose the R-related information

00:32:44.839 --> 00:32:53.239
in the submitted package. So that is the story of our R submission. We hope it has brought you

00:32:53.239 --> 00:32:58.920
some inspiration. And now I will hand over to Ning for a broader view in the industry.

