So starting with the plan within Roche, looking into the future. Right now, we are really,

00:33:18.119 --> 00:33:22.520
really excited about this first R end to end submission to health authorities and really

00:33:22.520 --> 00:33:29.719
happy to see that there hasn't been issues, technical issues so far. And as mentioned,

