of AI and especially large library modeling. And we are actively exploring how to use AI

00:34:44.120 --> 00:34:51.719
to assist programming, especially assist our code generation for clinical trial reporting.

00:34:51.719 --> 00:34:59.879
If you want to learn more, next week, September 17th, there will be our pharma gen AI day.

