Yeah. I think from our communication with the health authorities, we like plan to submit,

00:48:07.320 --> 00:48:15.159
we didn't hear anything about, like, requirements for QC. I think maybe we should be expecting the

00:48:15.159 --> 00:48:23.000
numbers, the analysis we include in our CSR or submit a document to be the accurate ones. So,

00:48:23.399 --> 00:48:32.679
yeah, so we didn't meet something question like QC should be done in some certain way.

00:48:32.679 --> 00:48:37.560
Yeah, I feel like, again, kind of like reflecting, kind of like citing the same

00:48:37.560 --> 00:48:43.239
clarification statement from FDA, they are not asking for any specific programming language. So

00:48:43.239 --> 00:48:48.199
I don't expect they will ask for QC, you know, specific programming language. Yeah.

